    <section class="mt-96" id="Summary">
      <div
        class="flex flex-col-reverse md:flex-row items-center p-4 md:p-20 bg-white dark:bg-lightBlack space-y-8 md:space-y-0 md:space-x-8"
      >
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 my-10">
          <h1 class="text-black dark:text-white text-4xl md:text-5xl my-4">
            Who We Are
          </h1>
          <p class="text-grey my-10 text-xs md:text-sm">
            SpaceXShares is a subsidiary company of
            <a
              class="text-darkBlue dark:text-lightBlue hover:underline font-bold"
              href="https://www.spacex.com/"
              target="_blank"
            >
              SpaceX</a
            >, the aerospace company founded by visionary entrepreneur Elon Musk
            in 2002. The company is based in Hawthorne, California and
            specializes in developing and manufacturing advanced rockets and
            spacecraft for missions ranging from delivering satellites into
            orbit to transporting humans to other planets. <br />
            <br />
            <br />
            As a subsidiary of SpaceX, SpaceXShares focuses on the investment
            and shares aspect of the company's operations. The company offers
            investors the opportunity to invest in SpaceX and participate in the
            company's success by purchasing shares of SpaceX stock or in any
            other available company shares. This provides a unique opportunity
            for individuals and organizations to get involved with one of the
            most innovative and forward-thinking companies in the world.
            SpaceXShares is committed to providing investors with transparent
            and comprehensive information about SpaceX's financial performance
            and future plans. This includes regular updates on the company's
            progress towards its goals, as well as detailed financial reports
            and projections. With a team of experienced and knowledgeable
            investment professionals, SpaceXShares is dedicated to helping
            investors make informed decisions and achieve their financial goals.
            <br />
            <br />
            <br />
            Overall, SpaceXShares represents an exciting opportunity for
            investors to get involved with a company that is at the forefront of
            space exploration and technology. As a subsidiary of SpaceX, the
            company has access to some of the most advanced technologies and
            talented professionals in the industry, making it a compelling
            choice for anyone interested in investing in the future of space
            exploration and innovation.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
          <img
            class="mt-10"
            src="../Images/elonMusk.jpg"
            alt="This is an Image."
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section id="Values">
      <div
        class="flex flex-col-reverse md:flex-row p-4 md:p-20 dark:bg-lightBlue bg-darkBlue space-y-8 md:space-y-0 md:space-x-8"
      >
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
          <img
            class="my-10"
            src="../Images/Building-5.jpg"
            alt="This is an Image."
          />
        </div>
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 mt-10">
          <h1 class="dark:text-black text-white text-4xl md:text-5xl my-4">
            Our Values
          </h1>
          <h4 class="mt-10 text-base md:text-lg dark:text-black text-white">
            Our Mission
          </h4>
          <p class="text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-700 text-xs md:text-sm mt-4">
            To provide accessible and profitable investment opportunities in the
            space industry through the trading of shares in both SpaceX and
            other space-related ventures.
          </p>
          <h4 class="mt-10 text-base md:text-lg dark:text-black text-white">
            Our Vision
          </h4>
          <p class="text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-700 text-xs md:text-sm mt-4">
            To be a leading investment company in the space industry, driving
            innovation and growth through strategic investment and
            collaboration.
          </p>
          <h4 class="mt-10 text-base md:text-lg dark:text-black text-white">
            Our Goal
          </h4>
          <p class="text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-700 text-xs md:text-sm mt-4">
            To provide investors with significant returns on investment through
            the trading of shares in space-related ventures. To foster
            innovation and technological advancement in the space industry
            through strategic investment and collaboration with leading space
            companies. To support the development of a sustainable and
            profitable space industry that benefits humanity and the planet.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
